	<contentText >
		<text  style="line-height: 18px;font-size: 14px;" ><![CDATA[Several days after Emma posts Sandy’s story to her blog, she's contacted by a local celebrity who wants to help with Sandy's medical costs. In a phone conversation with the celebrity, Emma discovers that she's also a customer. A manager from another department, Tom, overhears her conversation and later approaches her.]]></text>
	</contentText>
